    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA345-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu teḷiviṭai vilakkiyatu (ER, EV: vilaṅkiyatu).</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is what checked [HER] in the time of confidence.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA345">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            kāṉaṟ kaṇṭaṟ kaḻaṉṟuku paiṅkāy</l>
<l>            nīṉiṟa viruṅkaḻi yuṭpaṭa vīḻnteṉa</l>
<l>            vuṟukā ṟūkkat tūṅki yāmpal</l>
<l>            ciṟuveṇ kākkai yāvit taṉṉa</l>
<l>            veḷiya viriyun tuṟaiva veṉṟu</l>
<l>            maḷiya periyōr kēṇmai numpōṟ</l>
<l>            cālpetir koṇṭa cemmai yōrun</l>
<l>            tēṟā neñcaṅ kaiyaṟupu vāṭa</l>
<l>            nīṭiṉṟu virumpā rāyiṉ</l>
<l>            vāḻtaṉmaṟ ṟevaṉō tēykamā teḷivē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>            O man from the ghat, where the white ones are expanding,</l>
<l rend="indent2">            as if the little white crow yawned,</l>
<l rend="indent">            the white waterlilies, hanging while the coming wind lifts [them],</l>
<l rend="indent2">            as<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">vīḻnteṉa</term>: here it does not make sense to understand the form in a causal sense. Why not, actually, take it as an infinitive?</note> the fresh unripe fruits shed loose from the seashore grove’s</l>
<l rend="indent2">             mangrove</l>
<l rend="indent2">            fall so that they plunge into the big backwaters of blue colour,</l>
<l>        pitiful [are] friendships with great people like you.</l>
<l rend="indent">            If they do not long for a long time,</l>
<l rend="indent2">            so that the unbelieving heart fades into motionlessness,</l>
<l rend="indent3">            even in impartial ones that received quality,<note place="foot">What is this line supposed to express? Even a more patient and less lovelorn woman then HER would have lost her temper when confronted with HIS behaviour?</note></l>
<l>        what of but living?</l>
<l rend="indent4">            May the great clarity dwindle.        </l>
</lg>
      </div>
    </body>
